      <title>据称达利欧在桥水基金的离职条款将推迟阿布扎比计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/dalio-s-exit-terms-at-bridgewater-said-to-delay-abu-dhabi-plans</link>
