    <item>
      <title>铜价创三个月新低，中国需求成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/metals-mixed-after-weekly-slump-as-china-cuts-short-term-rate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铜价下跌，因基本金属延续近两年来最严重的周跌幅，而中国小幅降息也未能缓解人们对全球最大大宗商品消费国需求的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/metals-mixed-after-weekly-slump-as-china-cuts-short-term-rate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 04:38:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员关注拜登退欧后美国期货价格上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/dollar-edges-lower-following-biden-s-election-exit-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者的目光不再局限于乔·拜登结束总统连任竞选，而是主要关注企业收益，美国科技股有望从 4 月份以来最糟糕的一周中反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/dollar-edges-lower-following-biden-s-election-exit-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 22:55:51 GMT</pubDate>
